&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with clients to help upgrade their Access safety measures.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Enjoy site visits to view progression and completion of the large projects.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with all our different teams to collaborate across a wide range of projects.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/li&gt;
