&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Overview&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Reporting to the Assistant Controller, the Accounting Manager - Tax, will bring deep expertise in U.S. GAAP and domestic and international tax compliance matters while serving as a key contributor within Jensen Hughes’ Accounting team. This role oversees international compliance activities, including statutory audits, and supports the company’s global tax function across corporate income tax, VAT, sales and use tax, and transfer pricing matters. The role also maintains responsibility for accounting related to the company’s global lease portfolio.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;In addition to technical expertise, this position plays an important role in developing and supporting team members, fostering collaboration, and building strong relationships with internal leadership, external advisors, and stakeholders across the organization. Jensen Hughes values diverse perspectives, thoughtful leadership, and a collaborative approach to problem-solving.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Responsibilities&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead, coach, and support a team of one to three Senior Accountants, with a focus on professional development, collaboration, and continuous improvement.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage international statutory audits across multiple global regions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist with international compliance matters, including statutory licensing and ratings requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support all facets of the company’s tax function, including:
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preparing U.S. corporate income tax support and partnering with external tax providers for annual filings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing the execution of corporate income tax payments related to annual returns, estimated payments, and extensions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Coordinating and resolving corporate income tax notices and inquiries.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Managing monthly and quarterly VAT compliance activities for the Middle East region.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting state and local tax compliance activities, including sales and use tax, gross receipts, and personal property taxes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assisting with international tax matters in partnership with local finance teams and external advisors.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
