&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Risk-Informed Applications&lt;/strong&gt; – supporting licensing and regulatory strategies that impact plant operations (e.g., RICT, 50.69, ILRT extensions)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Tools &amp;amp; Innovation&lt;/strong&gt; – applying online risk tools and exploring advanced methods, including optimization approaches&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Human Reliability &amp;amp; Accident Analysis&lt;/strong&gt; – conducting HRA and evaluating severe accident scenarios&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Advanced Nuclear&lt;/strong&gt; – supporting regulatory and risk initiatives for next-generation nuclear (e.g., NEI 18-04, LMP, ESP and siting)&lt;/li&gt;
